OL,3,C'Addicted': The teenagers who gave up
OL,4,Ctheir phones for a fortnight
OL,6,FAfter weeks of planning with Beaulieu
OL,7,FSchool we launched an experiment
OL,8,Ftaking phones away from unknowing
OL,9,Fpupils for a fortnight.
OL,11,FIn the weeks running up to the day, we
OL,12,Fasked for permission from parents
OL,13,Fwithout the children's knowledge. Out
OL,14,Fof 90 girls in the year group, only 11
OL,15,Fof their parents agreed.
OL,17,FWhen the girls entered the room with
OL,18,Ftheir phones, they had no idea they
OL,19,Fwould be leaving without them.
