OL,3,C'Addicted': The teenagers who gave up
OL,4,Ctheir phones for a fortnight
OL,6,FThat being said - all of them agreed
OL,7,Fto take part with one of them saying
OL,8,F"I know I'm addicted - I know I am.
OL,9,FIt's just no one has ever tried to
OL,10,Fstop me."
OL,12,FBefore saying their goodbyes, I wanted
OL,13,Fto know how much time they spend
OL,14,Fscrolling and messaging on each day.
OL,16,FThe highest average daily screen time
OL,17,Fwas five hours and 58 minutes - or a
OL,18,Fquarter of her day. For context, that
OL,19,Fis higher than my own screen time as a
OL,20,Fjournalist using a phone for work.
