OL,3,C'Addicted': The teenagers who gave up
OL,4,Ctheir phones for a fortnight
OL,6,FAnother student went on to tell me
OL,7,Fthat she had once spent 23 hours in a
OL,8,Fweek solely on TikTok.
OL,10,FI asked them if they had come across
OL,11,Fany harmful content while scrolling
OL,12,Fonline, and their answers ranged from
OL,13,Fcontent and comments about suicide to
OL,14,Fsexually inappropriate material - and
OL,15,Fa reminder that these students are
OL,16,Fjust 13 and 14 years old.
