OL,3,C'Addicted': The teenagers who gave up
OL,4,Ctheir phones for a fortnight
OL,6,FResearch by the Children's
OL,7,FCommissioner for England says almost
OL,8,Fthree-quarters of teenagers between 13
OL,9,Fand 17 have encountered one or more
OL,10,Fpotential harms online.
OL,12,FMeanwhile the average age at which
OL,13,Fchildren first see pornography is just
OL,14,F13 years old.
