OL,3,C'Addicted': The teenagers who gave up
OL,4,Ctheir phones for a fortnight
OL,6,FThe UK Act involves a series of rules
OL,7,Faiming to protect children from
OL,8,Fcontent relating to topics including
OL,9,Fsuicide, self-harm, eating disorders
OL,10,Fand pornography.
OL,12,FBeaulieu teacher Mr Harris hopes the
OL,13,FITV News experiment can help highlight
OL,14,Fhow difficult it is to control what
OL,15,Fchildren can access online.
OL,17,FHe told ITV News: "I've got an 11-year-
OL,18,Fold at home, who will be starting
OL,19,Fsecondary school in September, and
OL,20,Fhe's just got his phone.
